+
+    After iteration shift analysis:
+    - Iteration i writes A[i%2]
+    - Iteration i+1 reads A[(i+1)%2] (shifted from A[i%2])
+    - A[i%2] vs A[(i+1)%2] are disjoint (0 vs 1 or 1 vs 0), so no dependency
+    """
